    <item>
      <title>数据中心高管现正寻求筹集 5 亿美元，用于投资房车存储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/data-center-executive-seeks-500-million-for-rv-storage-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加里·沃伊塔泽克 (Gary Wojtaszek) 将数据中心公司 CyrusOne 打造成了一家巨头，然后以约 150 亿美元的价格将其出售给 KKR &amp; Co. 和 Global Infrastructure Partners。现在，他正在寻求 5 亿美元的资金来进行另一种赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/data-center-executive-seeks-500-million-for-rv-storage-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本计划限制芯片和量子计算技术的出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/japan-plans-to-curb-exports-of-chips-quantum-computing-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本扩大出口管制范围，将尖端芯片和量子计算机相关技术纳入其中，中国警告称，此举可能对两国贸易产生负面影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/japan-plans-to-curb-exports-of-chips-quantum-computing-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊密西西比数据中心价格上涨 60% 至 160 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/amazon-mississippi-data-center-costs-jump-to-16-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司预计将在密西西比州的大型数据中心项目上花费比之前宣布的金额高出 60%，这凸显了人工智能基础设施成本的不断上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/amazon-mississippi-data-center-costs-jump-to-16-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Charter 宽带用户流失加剧有线电视困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/charter-s-broadband-subscriber-losses-add-to-woe-for-cable-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Charter Communications Inc. 第四季度损失了 177,000 名宽带用户，在互联网接入市场竞争激烈的情况下，这一情况比预期更糟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/charter-s-broadband-subscriber-losses-add-to-woe-for-cable-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:25:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 的扎克伯格凭借在创新方面超越竞争对手的历史，挑战 DeepSeek</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-31/meta-s-zuckerberg-takes-on-deepseek-with-history-of-topping-innovative-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欢迎阅读 Tech In Depth，这是我们新版的每日新闻通讯，其中包含来自彭博社全球记者对科技业务的报道和分析。今天，Kurt Wagner 写道，一家中国初创公司以较低成本开发的人工智能模型的出现可能会对 Meta Platforms Inc. 有利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-31/meta-s-zuckerberg-takes-on-deepseek-with-history-of-topping-innovative-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:05:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芯片业务低迷，意法半导体计划裁员 3000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/stmicro-eyes-workforce-cuts-of-up-to-6-as-chip-slump-drags-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于面临工业和汽车领域长期需求低迷，意法半导体 (STMicroelectronics NV) 正考虑通过提前退休和自然减员的方式将员工人数减少约 6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/stmicro-eyes-workforce-cuts-of-up-to-6-as-chip-slump-drags-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 11:59:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
